features: The Flow Box Co. introduces our feminine care product organizer.

Made with durable plastic, this tampon, pad and liner organizer is a great alternative to cardboard boxes for tampon or sanitary pad storage. We want to see more options for feminine care storage other than plastic bags and cardboard boxes. Here is an alternative!
Lightweight for home or travel use. You can bring with you on the go, store under your sink, or in your cabinet.
Hinged lid to keep your feminine care products clean and sanitary as well as keeping little hands from breaking and entering!
Colorful options for fun or discreet feminine care storage! Whether you want to keep your flow box discreet or vibrant, we have options for you!
body.description: This product is a feminine care product organizer for your sanitary products. A great alternative to cardboard boxes and plastic bags for feminine care storage. Perfect for keeping your sanitary pads, tampons and liners in a discreet, easy to use box. Very lightweight with durable plastic. You can store on your countertop, under the sink, your room or anywhere you desire. We have 3 colors to choose from, whether you want to be more discreet or colorful! We aim to provide more options for women to store their feminine care products in an organized fashion!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I got this for my wife because we were tired of seeing the bag of her pads and my daughter asking about them. It is actually petite and cleaner than I thought. I really like the color. It’s more of a baby blue than a mint green and it makes sour bathroom look so much cleaner.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pretty and Perfect Size
reviews.reviewText: This is exactly what I needed to store my backup when shark week hits. I wanted something to discretely store my pads and tampons in my office at work. It holds a whole bunch of tampons plus a couple pads. You can honestly use it for anything. It fits nicely in my desk drawer or I could leave it on my shelf. Highly recommend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pretty and practical but it comes empty!!!!!
reviews.reviewText: I got this plastic container to offer some pads for our office's clients in case of emergency. It is very discrete and will do the job being placed under the bathroom sink.Even though the seller clearly specifies measurements, it is smaller than the image, fyi.I may not be the only one but I am posting the following info just in case:THE BOX DOES NOT INCLUDE PADS OR TAMPONS!!! It comes empty so you need to get those yourself. I am not complaining. I am just suggesting for the seller to notify buyers of this detail on the description like""Feminine products not included" or something to that effect. If you do, I apologize in advance however it's not as accessible as it should be if that is the case. At any rate, cute and useful item.
